{
  "stem": "11175.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we went over to that man which he lived in the same building-- in the same house-- house, and we said, Mr.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Wassakela, what we gonna-- his name was Wassakela.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We said-- we said, Wassakela, what we have to do?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We want to go out to work.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We don't want to stay like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he said to us, you wait here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I'm gonna go-- I'm not afraid.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You see, I'm gonna go out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They know me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I will find out from the [INAUDIBLE] Konrad-- he knew Konrad, the leader from the SS from the [INAUDIBLE] in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He knew-- he said, I'm gonna go over to Konrad and ask Konrad what I should do with my people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I have the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So he went out, and he said, don't move from here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You stay and wait.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And about 15, 20 minutes, he came back.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He said, I just had an order to take my people and to go over to the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] was the most-- from the welterfassen.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If you came into that street, you were a little bit more secured because they-- the SS and the Ukraine, it they didn't came into that street to take out some people because this was under the jurisdiction from Mr.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Konrad, and nobody can come in to that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he came out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He come over to us, and he-- he told us about going out to work that we organize ourselves.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We put ourselves about-- about 10 or 15 groups, four-- the four people walking, you know, in a line, and we start to march out.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We marched out from 40-- from the-- from the gate from 46, going over to the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
